download_smos           Download BEC-SMOS soil moisture data
extract_smos            Extract BEC-SMOS soil moisture estimates for
                        specific geographical locations
find_smos               Find BEC-SMOS soil moisture data in Barcelona
                        Expert Center (BEC) server
list_smos               List the BEC-SMOS data files stored on a local
                        computer
missing_smos            Print the dates for which BEC-SMOS soil
                        moisture data have not been found
plot_raster_smos        Draw a raster image of BEC-SMOS soil moisture
                        data
plot_temporal_smos      Plot temporal series of BEC-SMOS soil moisture
                        data
set_credentials         Set credentials to access Barcelona Expert
                        Center (BEC) server
